hackathon-description-text: VikeHacks is Lynbrook High School's student hackathon. Join us for 12 hours of hacking, learning, and prizes!
hackathon-eligibility: Only students at Lynbrook High School may participate
hackathon-rules:
All attendees, sponsors, partners, volunteers and staff at our hackathon are required to agree with the following code of conduct. Organisers will enforce this code throughout the event. We expect cooperation from all participants to ensure a safe environment for everybody.
You can find the Hack Code of Conduct here: https://hackcodeofconduct.org/
